53
00:05:17,901 --> 00:05:19,820
Yeah, I just don't have
anything for you, Kevin.

54
00:05:19,903 --> 00:05:21,363
Well, boss, when I signed up, you said…

55
00:05:21,446 --> 00:05:22,948
